rmalTextRun SCXP243999763 BCX0\\">: nouer des partenariats avec des collectivit&eacute;s volontaires afin d&rsquo;approfondir le travail sur les donn&eacute;es territoriales (donn&eacute;es cadastrales, cartographie des destinations&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\\"TextRun SCXP243999763 BCX0\\" lang=\\"FR-FR\\" xml:lang=\\"FR-FR\\" data-scheme-color=\\"@5B9BD5,8,\\" data-usefontface=\\"true\\" data-contrast=\\"none\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXP243999763 BCX0\\">etc.). Vous &ecirc;tes une collectivit&eacute; et souhaitez approfondir le sujet ? Contactez-nous !</span></span></span></p>\\n<h2 class=\\"Paragraph SCXP243999763 BCX0\\" lang=\\"EN-US\\" xml:lang=\\"EN-US\\" data-ccp-props=\\"{&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559731&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335562764&quot;:2,&quot;335562765&quot;:1,&quot;335562766&quot;:4,&quot;335562767&quot;:0,&quot;335562768&quot;:4,&quot;335562769&quot;:0}\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt;\\"><span class=\\"TextRun SCXP243999763 BCX0\\" lang=\\"FR-FR\\" xml:lang=\\"FR-FR\\" data-scheme-color=\\"@5B9BD5,8,\\" data-usefontface=\\"true\\" data-contrast=\\"none\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXP243999763 BCX0\\">&Agrave; venir</span></span></span></h2>\\n</div>\\n<div class=\\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXP243999763 BCX0\\">\\n<p class=\\"Paragraph SCXP243999763 BCX0\\" lang=\\"EN-US\\" xml:lang=\\"EN-US\\" data-ccp-props=\\"{&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559731&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335562764&quot;:2,&quot;335562765&quot;:1,&quot;335562766&quot;:4,&quot;335562767&quot;:0,&quot;335562768&quot;:4,&quot;335562769&quot;:0}\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt;\\"><span class=\\"TextRun SCXP243999763 BCX0\\" lang=\\"FR-FR\\" xml:lang=\\"FR-FR\\" data-usefontface=\\"true\\" data-contrast=\\"none\\"><span class=\\"NormalTextRun SCXP243999763 BCX0\\">D&eacute;mo</span></spa